'''滑板运动'''是一种包含滑行和用[[滑板|滑板]]表演[[杂技|杂技]]的[[极限运动|极限运动]]，它也是一种休闲活动，一种艺术，一项职业，还是一种[[交通工具|交通工具]]<ref>{{cite web|title=Extreme Market Research|url=http://www.webdelsol.com/Topic/articles/04/howell.html|work=Topic Magazine|publisher=Topic Magazine|accessdate=August 17, 2012|author=Ocean Howell|year=2003|archive-date=2018-02-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180207195518/http://www.webdelsol.com/Topic/articles/04/howell.html|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。多年来这项运动影响了众多人口。一项2009年的报告显示全球共有110.8万滑板运动爱好者，这个市场的年收入估计为48亿美元<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.shop-eat-surf.com/2009/05/the-state-of-the-skateboarding-industry |title=The state of the skateboarding industry |date=May 12, 2009 |accessdate=July 23, 2014 |first=Tiffany |last=Montgomery |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140812232423/http://www.shop-eat-surf.com/2009/05/the-state-of-the-skateboarding-industry/ |archivedate=2014年8月12日 |df= }}</ref>。從1970年代開始就有為喜歡玩滑板、自由式車手、職業級的車手精心設置的滑板場地<ref>{{cite web | url=http://skateboard.about.com/cs/boardscience/a/brief_history_2.htm | title=Skateboarding: A Brief History (page 2) | accessdate=December 13, 2006 | author=Steve Cave, [[about.com|about.com]] | archive-date=2007-02-14 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20070214071941/http://skateboard.about.com/cs/boardscience/a/brief_history_2.htm | dead-url=no }}</ref>。

==安全==
滑板像其他小轮交通工具（如[[直排轮|直排轮]]或[[滑板车|滑板车]]）一样都有一个安全问题：当遇到路面凹凸不平，尤其是有与滑行方向垂直的裂缝时，玩家容易被甩出，这是从滑板上跌下受伤的主因<ref name="Fountain-1996">{{Cite journal  | last1 = Fountain | first1 = JL. | last2 = Meyers | first2 = MC. | title = Skateboarding injuries. | journal = Sports Med | volume = 22 | issue = 6 | pages = 360–6 |date=Dec 1996 | doi =  10.2165/00007256-199622060-00004| PMID = 8969014 }}</ref>。

重傷較為少見，通常是由跌倒造成的擦傷、割傷、瘀傷、扭傷<ref name="Keilani-2010">{{Cite journal  | last1 = Keilani | first1 = M. | last2 = Krall | first2 = C. | last3 = Lipowec | first3 = L. | last4 = Posch | first4 = M. | last5 = Komanadj | first5 = TS. | last6 = Crevenna | first6 = R. | title = Skateboarding injuries in Vienna: location, frequency, and severity. | journal = PM R | volume = 2 | issue = 7 | pages = 619–24 |date=Jul 2010 | doi = 10.1016/j.pmrj.2010.04.022 | PMID = 20659717 }}</ref>；半数需入院的伤者为骨折，伤到的通常是手臂和腿部的长骨<ref name="Fountain-1996" />。三分之一的伤者是玩了不到一星期的新手。<ref name="Fountain-1996" />伤情较重者会有[[头部外伤|头部外伤]]，甚至死亡。虽然发生这种情况的概率较低，但也有3.5%到9%<ref name="Fountain-1996" />。

使用滑板作为交通工具会使玩家处于其他交通工具的危险中。在街上玩滑板会被其他的车撞，或者跌入车流中。玩家也会给其他行人和车辆带来危险。一旦玩家跌倒，滑板可能会滑向或飞向另一个人。滑板撞到行人或骑自行车的人后会使之受伤甚至死亡（虽然这比较罕见）<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.mercurynews.com/breaking-news/ci_18443561 |title=Woman killed after collision with skateboarder had been hit by one 15 years prior |author=White, Kimberly |newspaper=San Jose Mercury News |date=July 11, 2011 |accessdate=2015-07-04 |archive-date=2012-01-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120121220614/http://www.mercurynews.com/breaking-news/ci_18443561 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

许多地方的法规要求玩滑板时必须戴上自行车[[头盔|头盔]]以降低头部受伤和死亡的风险。护腕也是可以减少受伤可能性的保护器械。有医学研究者建议只能在特别指定的地方玩滑板，这样能减少受伤人数，降低受伤程度，并可避免由机动车造成的伤害以及给其他行人造成的伤害。<ref name="Fountain-1996" />。

挪威曾因为伤害事故频发，从1978年到1989年禁止使用、拥有和销售滑板。面对这一禁令，有玩家在森林和其他隐秘场所里建设坡道，以此逃避警察<ref>{{cite journal |last=Forsman |first=L. |last2=Eriksson |first2=A. |title=Skateboarding injuries of today |date=June 26, 2001 |journal=British Journal of Sports Medicine |publisher=BMJ Publishing Group |volume=35 |pages=325–328 |url=http://bjsportmed.com/content/35/5/325.full |doi=10.1136/bjsm.35.5.325 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130120134908/http://bjsportmed.com/content/35/5/325.full |archivedate=2013年1月20日 }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |url=http://news.google.com/newspapers?nid=1755&dat=19780914&id=sAAkAAAAIBAJ&sjid=hGcEAAAAIBAJ&pg=5528,6154421 |title=Norway to Ban Skateboards |date=September 14, 1978 |publisher=Sarasota Herald-Tribune |accessdate=October 13, 2012 |archive-date=2016-04-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160424133551/https://news.google.com/newspapers?nid=1755&dat=19780914&id=sAAkAAAAIBAJ&sjid=hGcEAAAAIBAJ&pg=5528,6154421 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

==滑板技巧 ==
{{Main|滑板}}
滑板的基本動作有滑行、轉彎、停止；滑板的花式動作可分為地板花式（JUMP & FLIP）、竿上花式（Slide & grind），其中地板花式有豚跳（Ollie）、腳尖翻板（Kickflip）、腳跟翻板（Heelflip）等技巧動作，竿上花式有前板身（Front Side Board Slide）、後板身（Back Side Board Slide）等技巧動作。

於2012年由{{link-en|湯姆·沙爾Tom Schaar}}首次登場最新進展{{link-en|1080 (滑板技巧)|1080 (skateboarding)|1080}}種滑板技巧的招式<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.skateboarding.com.au/news/12-year-old-lands-first-ever-1080-skateboard/|title=12 year old lands the first ever 1080 on a skateboard|date=July 3, 2012|publisher=Skateboarding.com.au|accessdate=October 7, 2012|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121215175336/http://www.skateboarding.com.au/news/12-year-old-lands-first-ever-1080-skateboard/|archive-date=2012-12-15|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.redbull.com/cs/Satellite/en_INT/Video/tom-schaar-first-ever-1080-video-021243187489113 |date=March 30, 2012 |title=12-year-old skateboarder nails first ever 1080 |format=video |publisher=Red Bull |accessdate=April 3, 2012 |archive-date=2012-05-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120501095403/http://www.redbull.com/cs/Satellite/en_INT/Video/tom-schaar-first-ever-1080-video-021243187489113 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

